indimail-mta (2.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * use packetsize > 512 to avoid dkim failures for sites having long txt records (hotmail.com)
  * config-fast removed display of DESTDIR
  * svscanboot/svscan option run .svscan/run or INITCMD. Use unshare --mount option to mount private mounts like custom resolv.conf
  * svscan - run .svscan/shutdown on SIGTERM
  * added inotify program to get file system events
  * added resolvconf service

 -- Manvendra Bhangui <manvendra@indimail.org>  Fri, 12 May 2017 17:54:40 +0530
